utide</td><td><span class=\"highlight\">-18.7%</span></td><td>46週</td><td>2</td><td>MASH改善62%</td></tr><tr><td>orforglipron</td><td><span class=\"highlight\">-12.4%</span></td><td>72週</td><td>3</td><td>経口投与</td></tr></table><div class=\"alert-box\">注：試験Phase・期間・対象が異なるため単純比較は不可</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
